{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit/about","content_id":"5f5ad218-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","description":"The Export Control Joint Unit (ECJU) administers the UK’s system of export controls and licensing for military and dual-use items.","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p><abbr title=\"Export Control Joint Unit\">ECJU</abbr> brings together operational and policy expertise from the Department for Business and Trade (<abbr title=\"Department for Business and Trade\">DBT</abbr>), Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office (<abbr title=\"Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office\">FCDO</abbr>) and the Ministry of Defence (<abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr>).</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"responsibilities\">Responsibilities</h2>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Department for Business and Trade\">DBT</abbr> has overall responsibility for the statutory and regulatory framework of export controls, and for decisions to grant or refuse an export licence.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Foreign, Commonwealth and Development Office\">FCDO</abbr> and <abbr title=\"Ministry of Defence\">MOD</abbr> are <abbr title=\"Department for Business and Trade\">DBT</abbr>’s principal advisers, advising on the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://questions-statements.parliament.uk/written-statements/detail/2021-12-08/hcws449\">Strategic Export Licensing Criteria</a>, which are used to assess licence applications.</p>\n\n<p>We aim to deliver an efficient, rigorous and customer-friendly export licensing and compliance service.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"Changed reference from Consolidated EU and National Arms Export Licensing Criteria to Strategic Export Licensing Criteria.","public_timestamp":"2021-12-09T09:02:33Z"},{"note":"Updated the description and responsibilities of the export control joint unit.","public_timestamp":"2018-06-22T15:01:16Z"},{"note":"Revised text to reflect creation of export control joint unit.","public_timestamp":"2017-11-02T09:57:27Z"},{"note":"Priorities text updated.","public_timestamp":"2016-08-22T15:16:58Z"},{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2016-08-22T12:26:38Z"},{"note":"Text updated to reflect changes in government departments.","public_timestamp":"2016-08-22T12:26:38Z"}],"corporate_information_groups":[],"headers":[{"id":"responsibilities","level":2,"text":"Responsibilities"}],"organisation":"183520bb-7f82-487d-91d4-bb079cc259a2","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"about","first_published_at":"2016-08-22T14:26:38+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit/about","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit/about","base_path":"/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit/about","content_id":"5f5ad218-7631-11e4-a3cb-005056011aef","document_type":"about","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2021-12-09T09:02:33Z","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","title":"About us","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit/about","withdrawn":false}],"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT557","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit","base_path":"/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit","content_id":"183520bb-7f82-487d-91d4-bb079cc259a2","details":{"acronym":"ECJU","brand":"department-for-business-trade","default_news_image":null,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Export Control Joint Unit"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Export Control Joint Unit","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/export-control-joint-unit","withdrawn":false}],"taxons":